data.text: @MKEhealth @CDCgov When can we start an approach to monitoring Fentanyl Overdoses in our communities? Milwaukee is in HIGH ALERT 🚨 RED of 600+ fentanyl overdoses in 2021. How can we shift into 2022 pledging for lives? MAF MOTHER’S AGAINST FENTANYL https://t.co/KIfSXCcSAV
@CDCgov Learn more about the COVID-19 Community Levels at https://t.co/xClDHob4vJ https://t.co/hm4zKNHzGD

@CDCgov COVID-19 Community Level is determined by looking at a combination of 3 metrics: 
➡ New COVID-19 hospital admissions per 100,000 in past 7 days
➡ 7-day average percent of staffed inpatient beds occupied by COVID-19 patients
➡ Total new COVID-19 cases per 100,000 in past 7 days https://t.co/buj6DhgTeA
